NewEvents:
- ID: 9005770
  Name: scale
  Comment: Applying the scaling speffect when a character is backread. X0_4 = entity id, X4_4 = speffect
  Commands:
  - IfCharacterBackreadStatus(MAIN, X0_4, true, ComparisonType.Equal, 1)
  - SetSpEffect(X0_4, X4_4)
  - IfCharacterBackreadStatus(MAIN, X0_4, false, ComparisonType.Equal, 1)
  - WaitFixedTimeSeconds(1)
  - EndUnconditionally(EventEndType.Restart)
  Tags: restart

- ID: 9005773
  Name: flagwarp
  Comment: Warp when X0_4 is turned on in the middle of things. X4_4 = warp target, X8_4 = warp map bytes, X12_4 = alternative flag, X16_4 = alternative warp target, X20_4 = alternate map bytes
  Commands:
  - GotoIfEventFlag(Label.Label0, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X0_4)
  - IfEventFlag(MAIN, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X0_4)
  - WaitFixedTimeSeconds(0.1)
  - ShowTextOnLoadingScreen(Disabled)
  - // Alt warp
  - GotoIfComparison(Label.Label2, ComparisonType.Equal, X12_4, 0)
  - GotoIfEventFlag(Label.Label2, OFF, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X12_4)
  - WarpPlayer(X20_1, X21_1, X22_1, X23_1, X16_4, 0)
  - GotoUnconditionally(Label.Label3)
  - // Main warp
  - Label2()
  - WarpPlayer(X8_1, X9_1, X10_1, X11_1, X4_4, 0)
  - // Probably don't need to do anything here?
  - Label3()
  - EndUnconditionally(EventEndType.End)
  - Label0()
  - SetEventFlag(TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X0_4, OFF)

- ID: 9005776
  Name: startboss
  Comment: >
    Sets event flag to start a boss fight in the given region, if the given boss flag is undefeated. X0_4 = boss defeat flag, X4_4 = trigger region, X8_4 = start flag
  Commands:
  - EndIfEventFlag(EventEndType.End, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X0_4)
  - IfInoutsideArea(MAIN, InsideOutsideState.Inside, 10000, X4_4, 1)
  - WaitFixedTimeFrames(1)
  - // WaitFixedTimeSeconds(X12_4) // Allow standing up first in some arenas
  - SetEventFlag(TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X8_4, ON)
  Tags: restart
- ID: 9005777
  Name: fogwarp
  Comment: >
    Takes an action prompt at a fog gate and warps to a target player, in the given map. X0_4 = fog gate, X4_4 = button param, X8_4 = warp target, X12_4 = warp map bytes, X16_4 = boss defeat flag (0 if not restricted), X20_4 = boss trap flag (0 if no defeat flag or no early escape). X24_4 = alternative flag, X28_4 = alternative warp target, X32_4 = alternate map bytes, X36_4 = rotate character target
  Commands:
  - // Wait for boss defeat, if flag is set
  - GotoIfComparison(Label.Label0, ComparisonType.Equal, X16_4, 0)
  - // Bypass boss check if trap flag not set
  - SkipIfComparison(1, ComparisonType.Equal, X20_4, 0)
  - GotoIfEventFlag(Label.Label0, OFF, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X20_4)
  - IfEventFlag(MAIN, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X16_4)
  - // Trigger for event. Starting with trap flag check
  - Label0()
  - GotoIfComparison(Label.Label1, ComparisonType.Equal, X20_4, 0)
  - GotoIfEventFlag(Label.Label1, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X16_4)
  - IfEventFlag(OR_01, ON, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X20_4)
  - // Actual detection
  - Label1()
  - IfActionButtonInArea(AND_05, X4_4, X0_4)
  - IfConditionGroup(OR_01, PASS, AND_05)
  - IfConditionGroup(MAIN, PASS, OR_01)
  - // Restart if no action button
  - EndIfConditionGroupStateCompiled(EventEndType.Restart, FAIL, AND_05)
  - // Restart if trapped
  - IfCharacterHasSpEffect(AND_06, 10000, 4280, false, ComparisonType.Equal, 1)
  - GotoIfConditionGroupStateUncompiled(Label.Label10, PASS, AND_06)
  - DisplayGenericDialog(90010, PromptType.OKCANCEL, NumberofOptions.OneButton, X0_4, 3)
  - WaitFixedTimeSeconds(1)
  - EndUnconditionally(EventEndType.Restart)
  - // Warping
  - // TODO, distinguish between fog gate cases and custom repeated warps (or use separate events)
  - // Also TODO, look at last parameter being set (depends on speffect 4250, which lasts for 3 seconds)
  - Label10()
  - RotateCharacter(10000, X36_4, 60060, false)
  - WaitFixedTimeSeconds(1)
  - ShowTextOnLoadingScreen(Disabled)
  - // Alt warp
  - GotoIfComparison(Label.Label2, ComparisonType.Equal, X24_4, 0)
  - GotoIfEventFlag(Label.Label2, OFF, TargetEventFlagType.EventFlag, X24_4)
  - WarpPlayer(X32_1, X33_1, X34_1, X35_1, X28_4, 0)
  - GotoUnconditionally(Label.Label3)
  - // Main warp
  - Label2()
  - WarpPlayer(X12_1, X13_1, X14_1, X15_1, X8_4, 0)
  - Label3()
  - WaitFixedTimeFrames(1)
  - EndUnconditionally(EventEndType.Restart)
